  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He went to-- to-- to-- to bring the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Didn't know I was in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I say, I would Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] When they start and say [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], who you are-- they didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- I-- I-- I was wondering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was too [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] so excited.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] I cannot talk one word to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That they are talking to me, and I couldn't answer them until my brother came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My brother came, and he saw the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then he said-- he talked to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] then you say to-- I did not-- I didn't answer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then they say to him, maybe he's a [? stimmer. ?] Maybe he can't talk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No, they said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When he came in the house, he said I would Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then my brother started again, talking, talking, talking to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Why, you know, I didn't answer till-- [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] and I said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] [SOBBING] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] Then, after this, I told him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He told me-- I-- I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he told me I would know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then, you know, then I told him-- he told me about everything-- how they killed mother, how they killed-- how they killed the sisters.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was know with everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I'm the first one-- but I have a long way for to get home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He told me-- all killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And now, it's happen with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] It's happened, a big miracle again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I came, we-- we was-- we-- I'm afraid to be in a small city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We ran to central [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
